    "ZPUSHNAME": "CMjm7tEGIABIAJABAPABAtgCvv6Vo9eflQM=",
    "ZMESSAGETYPE": 0,
    "ZTEXT": "Hello @244529936494832 \nThank you for the meeting and discussion regarding Bitrix24 improvements. Below is the summary of the agreed action items and next steps so that we can proceed with the implementation.\n\n*1. CRM Pipeline Stage Restructuring:*\nThe following stage names will replace the current pipeline stages:\n\nNew Lead\nAssigned\nNo Answer\nContacted / In Progress\nContact in Future\nMeeting Confirmed\nMeeting Attended\nOptions Sent\nReady to Buy\nDeal Closed\nNot Interested\nJunk (Job Seekers, Brokers, Service Providers, etc.)\nDeal Lost\n\n*2. Historical Lead Mapping*\nExisting leads and previous stage names should be mapped to the new pipeline stages to ensure continuity and reporting accuracy.\n\n*3. Sales Team Training*\nA one-hour training session will be conducted with the sales team to align everyone with the new pipeline structure and processes.\n\n*4. Go-Live Date*\nThe target date for implementing the changes is 29 June.\n\n*5. Zapier Integration Enhancement*\nStarting from 29 June, Zapier should capture and populate the following marketing attribution data into Bitrix:\n- Campaign Name\n- Ad Set Name\n- Ad Name\n\n*6. Duplicate Handling Process*\nWhen duplicate removal is applied:\n- The responsible user should receive a notification.\n- An activity should be automatically created in the CRM.\n- Proper end-to-end testing should be performed to validate the process.\n\n*7. Project and Branch Fields*\nIntroduce Project and Branch fields as list-type fields and expose them to Zapier for integration and automation purposes.\n\n*8. User Access Review*\nA complete list of users and their access permissions is required to review and validate the current setup.\n\n*9. Organizational Structure Review*\nThe current organizational structure in Bitrix needs to be reviewed and updated, as it does not reflect the latest organization hierarchy.\n\nPlease review the above and let us know if anything has been missed. Once confirmed, we can proceed with the implementation according to the agreed timeline.\n\nThank You",
    "ZSTANZAID": "3EB0778D2C084ADDF1FCA7",
